{
  "stem": "1062.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The scenery was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My village is in the foothills of the Carpathian Mountains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- and-- and the fields were lush and green and nice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And-- and, you know, we had to go to the forest to-- for-- for-- for wood, to make meals.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And as a child, I would go out in the-- in the-- in the woods and gather-- gather old branches to bring home for my mother to cook because there was no gas over there.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You know, we had to go and gather branches.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the forest didn't really have good wood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You know, they were poor forests.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But they had a lot of branches, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I would make bundles and bring it for my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And this is how she would cook.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But as I say, they were-- because since didn't know any better, they were happy days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "If I had a new-- a new-- a new pair of pants or a new suit or something like this, it was a big thing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You made a-- you made a [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You made a [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was a big-- but most of the time, what happened, it was passed along.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "In other words, I would-- when I grew up, my shirt, I would give it to my-- to my-- to my--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Brothers.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so-- and what they would also do is take-- like, in other words, if you-- if somebody had an old coat, they would take the old coat and turn it inside out so that, you know-- and there were tailors there, you know.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- and it was a project.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, just to make a coat, it would take a couple of weeks, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So-- so this is how you-- you had-- you had clothes.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
